title: Flight Simulator 2020 - How to - Cessna 172 - Set flight plan manually
description:
In this how to we are going to look how we can configure our flight plan manually in our navigation system from our  Cessna 172. Setting up the flight plan will also include using an SID and STAR as bonus.

Route being configure will be from Rotterdam Airport (EHRD) to Oostende/Brugge Airport (EBOS) initially.
